utility_evaluation.REASONING:
The required format includes 6 items: property, financing, legal_services, moving_services, setup_services, and total_budget. The final property solution contains all six items. Each one is fully specified with the expected details: 
- property: includes type, location, price, currency, bedrooms, bathrooms, accessibility and special features, and viewing time — fully detailed; 
- financing: includes purchase method, approval timeline, processing fees, and currency — fully specified; 
- legal_services: includes service name, cost, currency, and status — fully specified; 
- moving_services: includes service level, specialization, cost, currency, included features, timeline flexibility, and status — fully specified; 
- setup_services: includes utility package, cost, currency, services included, setup timeline, survey service and cost, and status — fully specified; 
- total_budget: includes all cost breakdowns, grand total, currency, budget fit, payment method, and timeline — fully specified. Therefore, all 6 out of 6 items are covered completely.
